PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Consumer and Corporate Affairs of Conrad Maheux, of Willowdale, Ontario, as a member of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years and designation of the said Conrad Maheux as Vice-President of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Hugh A. Krentz, whose term has expired.
